  m_text: "Khi m\u1EDBi ch\u01A1i, b\u1EA1n n\xEAn \u01B0u ti\xEAn l\xE0m quen v\u1EDBi
    ba thao t\xE1c quan tr\u1ECDng nh\u1EA5t: di chuy\u1EC3n, xoay camera v\xE0 t\u01B0\u01A1ng
    t\xE1c. Ch\u1EC9 c\u1EA7n n\u1EAFm ch\u1EAFc ba thao t\xE1c n\xE0y, b\u1EA1n
    \u0111\xE3 c\xF3 th\u1EC3 b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u x\u1EED l\xFD ph\u1EA7n l\u1EDBn
